## Module Objectives.

- Build a strong foundation in Python programming.
- Develop problem-solving skills through daily coding exercises.
- Learn clean code practices and modular program design.
- Prepare for advanced topics including NumPy, Pandas, SQL, and Machine Learning.

---

## Overview.

This module introduces the core building blocks of Python programming through progressively structured exercises.

The topics covered include:

- Variables and Data Types
- Operators
- Conditional Statements
- Loops
- Functions
- Lists
- Tuples
- Sets
- Dictionaries
- Strings
- File Handling
- Exception Handling
- Python Modules
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

Each topic includes practical examples focused on writing clean, readable, and well-structured code.

